on F</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0006-4971</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>56d82070c30e01.32497247</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>E0D2CB76-F56E-409E-A775-098B1DB51606</gtr:id><gtr:title>Determining the role of mononuclear phagocytes in prion neuroinvasion from the skin.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Journal of leukocyte biology</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/3d04b1b1ab33f684f37e71d0463f8dec"><gtr:id>3d04b1b1ab33f684f37e71d0463f8dec</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Wathne GJ</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0741-5400</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>56d820754533b5.76766234</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>AB7BEDB8-2024-440B-B3CA-EE3C2594E832</gtr:id><gtr:title>Expression of mesenchyme-specific gene signatures by follicular dendritic cells: insights from the meta-analysis of microarray data from multiple mouse cell populations.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Immunology</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/2671cbcc0eb0e80e6b60b9771fd2ad92"><gtr:id>2671cbcc0eb0e80e6b60b9771fd2ad92</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Mabbott NA</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2011-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0019-2805</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>56d8207631bd49.33375137</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>7DC2EE9A-0CA9-42CE-A093-E8BC853941B4</gtr:id><gtr:title>Immunology of Prion Protein and Prions.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Progress in molecular biology and translational science</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/2671cbcc0eb0e80e6b60b9771fd2ad92"><gtr:id>2671cbcc0eb0e80e6b60b9771fd2ad92</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Mabbott NA</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2017-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>1877-1173</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>5a85